                <head>5. Summary of Significant Discussion and Conclusions of a Policy Review
                    Committee Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d5fn1">Source: Carter
                        Library, National Security Council, Institutional Files, Box 41, Folder 3,
                            <gloss target="#t_PRM_1">PRM</gloss>–23 [3]. Top Secret; Talent Keyhole;
                        Comint. The meeting took place in the Old Executive Office Building.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1977-08-04T15:45:00-04:00" to="1977-08-04T17:45:00-04:00">August
